var e=JSON.parse(`[{"id":"L2_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"당연히 아시겠지만, 대정화전쟁 때 많은 사람들이 안타까운 비극을 겪었습니다.","JPN":"みんな知っていると思いますが、大浄化戦争で多くの人々が不運な悲劇を経験しました。","ENG":"As you may already know, many suffered unfortunate tragedies during the Great Purification War.","TWN":"如你所知，在大淨化戰爭期間，許多人遭遇了無可挽回的悲劇。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L3_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그땐 우리 모두가 피해자였고, 어린 아이들은 누군가의 도움 없인 살아남을 수 없었죠.","JPN":"あの時には私たちみんなが被害者で、幼い子どもたちは誰かの助けなしでは生き残れなかったのです。","ENG":"At that time, we were all victims. Young children could not survive unless someone assisted them.","TWN":"那時我們全都是受害者，年幼的孩子若沒有他人幫助，根本無法活下來。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L4_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이곳에서 생활하는 많은 자매들이 그 시절에 거둬들인 연고 없는 아이들입니다.","JPN":"ここで生活している多くの姉妹たちはあの頃に引き取った、家族なき子です。","ENG":"Many of the sisters who have settled here were the children from that era.","TWN":"在這裡生活的許多修女，都是當年收留的孤兒。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"프라이머 자매님도 그 중 한 명이죠.","JPN":"プライマー姉妹もその中の1人です。","ENG":"Sister Primer was also one of them.","TWN":"布萊伊莫修女也是其中之一。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"자매님은 어렸을 때부터 불의를 좌시하지 않는 올곧은 심성을 가지고 있었습니다.","JPN":"姉妹は小さい頃から不義から目を背けない、真っすぐな心を持っていました。","ENG":"From a young age, Sister Primer had a strong sense of justice.","TWN":"她從小就很正直，無法對不公不義視而不見。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L8_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"열 살 땐 몰래 외출을 나간 아이를 데려오다 폭력배들과 싸웠고…","JPN":"10歳の時にはこっそり家出した子を連れて帰る途中、ならず者とケンカし……","ENG":"At the age of ten, she fought against gangsters while bringing back the children who snuck out...","TWN":"十歲時，她曾為了帶回私自外出的孩子，與不良分子動手……"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"성인식을 치른 해엔 수도원을 점거하려던 극성테러 조직을 쫓아내기도 했어요.","JPN":"成人式の後には修道院を占拠しようとした過激テロ組織を追い払ったこともありました。","ENG":"And on the year of her coming of age ceremony, she even chased out a terrorist organization that was trying to take over the monastery.","TWN":"成年禮那年，甚至驅逐企圖佔領修道院的激進恐怖組織。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"물론 기특하고 자랑스럽지요. 프라이머 자매님을 보면 어떤 불의 앞에서도 고개를 돌리지 않을 거란 확신이 느껴졌습니다.","JPN":"もちろん健気で自慢に思います。プライマー姉妹を見ていると、どんな不義の前でも目を背けないという確信を感じました。","ENG":"Of course, I am proud of her. Looking at Sister Primer, I am confident that she would not turn her back on any injustice.","TWN":"當然，這樣的表現令人驕傲。每當看著布萊伊莫修女，我都覺得她絕不會在任何不義之事前低頭。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그렇기 때문에 난 늘 걱정이 앞섰어요. 자신이 감당하지 못할 무모한 정의는 결국 자신을 망가뜨리게 될 테니 말이죠.","JPN":"だからこそ私はいつも心配だったのです。手に負えない無謀な正義は、結局自分自身を壊すことになるはずですから。","ENG":"That is also why I am concerned about her. One day, she will destroy herself by attempting to handle justice she is incapable of handling.","TWN":"但也正因如此，我總是先替她感到擔心。因為無法承擔的魯莽正義，最終只會毀了自己。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그래서 성황청의 신부들이 찾아왔을 때, 저는 자매님이 시험을 치르게 했습니다.","JPN":"それで聖皇庁の神父たちが訪ねて来た時、私は姉妹に試験を受けさせました。","ENG":"So when the priests of the Holy Curia came to visit, I made Sister Primer take the test.","TWN":"所以當聖皇廳的神父來訪時，我讓她接受測試。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"정식 퇴마사가 되어 그에 걸맞은 힘을 기른다면, 그 정의로운 마음도 한층 견고해질 테니까요.","JPN":"正式のエクソシストになり、それ相応の力を養えば、正義に溢れる心も一段と強くなるはずでしょうから。","ENG":"If she were to become an official exorcist and gain the necessary strength, her righteousness would grow even stronger.","TWN":"若能成為正式的驅魔師、獲得相應的力量，那份正義之心也會更加堅定。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L14_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"조사를 했다면 아시겠지만, 퇴마사가 되는 것이 결코 쉬운 길은 아닙니다. 무엇보다 성황청의 인정을 받기 위한 세 가지 시험에서 통과해야 하죠.","JPN":"調べたらわかると思いますが、エクソシストになるのは決して簡単なことではありません。何より聖皇庁から認められるために、三つの試験で合格する必要があります。","ENG":"If you have done your research, you will understand that becoming an exorcist is not an easy task. Above all, one must pass three tests before being recognized by the Holy Curia.","TWN":"如果你調查過便會知道，成為驅魔師絕不是件容易的事，必須通過聖皇廳認可的三項測驗才行。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L15_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"프라이머 자매님은 비록 마지막 시험에서 떨어지긴 했지만, 신부님들께선 논의 끝에 자매님을 데려가기로 결정했습니다.","JPN":"プライマー姉妹は最後の試験で脱落してしまいましたが、神父たちは議論の末、姉妹を連れて行くことにしました。","ENG":"Sister Primer may have failed her final exam, but after much deliberation, the priests decided to accept her.","TWN":"雖然布萊伊莫修女在最後一項測驗失敗了，神父經過討論後仍決定帶走她。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L16_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아마도 앞선 두 가지 시험에서 충분히 퇴마사의 자질을 인정받았기 때문이겠지요.","JPN":"おそらくその前に二つの試験で、十分とエクソシストの資質を認めてもらったのでしょう。","ENG":"Perhaps it is because the previous two tests sufficiently demonstrated her qualifications to become an exorcist.","TWN":"大概是因為在前兩項測驗中，她已經充分證明了自己的資質吧。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"떨어진 마지막 시험이 뭐였냐고요?","JPN":"脱落した最後の試験は何だったのか気になりますか？","ENG":"What was the last test she failed, you ask?","TWN":"你問最後落敗的測驗是什麼啊？"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L18_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"후후, 우리 용감한 자매님도 무서워하는 게 하나쯤은 있거든요.","JPN":"ふふ、勇敢な姉妹にも怖いものが1つくらいあるのです。","ENG":"Haha, even the courageous Sister Primer is afraid of something.","TWN":"呵呵，我們那位勇敢的修女也有害怕的東西呢。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L21_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"어서오세요, 손님…","JPN":"いらっしゃいませ、お客様……","ENG":"Welcome to Gremory's Bar–","TWN":"歡迎光臨，客人……"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"으갸아아악!!!","JPN":"ふんぎゃあああぁっ！！！","ENG":"WHOAA!!","TWN":"呀啊啊啊！！！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L25_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"니콜이 그런 이상한 비명을 지르다니. 별일이구나.","JPN":"ニコルがそのような変な悲鳴をあげるとは。珍しいな。","ENG":"I didn't know Nicole could scream like that. How strange.","TWN":"妮可居然會發出那種奇怪的尖叫聲，還真少見。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"모모! 저기…가게에… 고양이가 들어왔어요!","JPN":"モモ！　あそこ……店に……猫が入ってきました！","ENG":"Momo! Th-there's... a c-cat... in the bar!","TWN":"莫莫！那個……店裡……有、有貓跑進來了！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"고양이?","JPN":"猫？","ENG":"A cat?","TWN":"貓？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L28_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"어머, 실례했어요. 아무래도 제 동료가 바텐더 아가씨를 겁준 모양이네요.","JPN":"あら、失礼。どうやら私の仲間がバーテンダーのお嬢さんを怖がらせてしまったようね。","ENG":"Oh, excuse me. It seems my little colleague scared your bartender.","TWN":"啊，不好意思。看來是我的同伴嚇到這位調酒師小姐了。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L29_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"냥?","JPN":"ニャ？","ENG":"Meow?","TWN":"喵？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L30_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"고양이를 데리고 다니는 수상한 손님이로구나. 정체를 밝히거라.","JPN":"猫を連れている怪しいお客さんだな。正体を明かせ。","ENG":"What a suspicious customer, bringing a cat to a bar. Reveal yourself!","TWN":"原來是帶著貓到處走的可疑客人啊？麻煩自我介紹一下。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L31_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"근처에서 카페를 운영하고 있는 직원이예요. 새 가게가 들어왔다길래, 이웃 분들에게 인사차 들렀답니다.","JPN":"この辺りのカフェで働いている職員だわ。新しい店ができたって聞いたから、ご近所さんに挨拶をしようと思って。","ENG":"I work at a nearby cafe. I came to say hello after hearing about the new bar that had opened.","TWN":"我是附近咖啡廳的員工。聽說這裡新開了一家店，就過來跟鄰居打聲招呼。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L33_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"혹시 그쪽이 점장님?","JPN":"もしかして、あなたが店長？","ENG":"Are you the manager?","TWN":"請問你是店長嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L34_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"점장 같은 하찮은 일은 이 몸의 하수인인 그레모리가 맡고 있지. 지금은 외출 중이니라.","JPN":"店長のようなくだらない仕事は吾輩の下僕、グレモリーが受け持っている。今は外出中だ。","ENG":"Tedious tasks like managing are done by my subject, Gremory. But she's out right now.","TWN":"店長那種瑣碎的工作，是交給我的手下葛茉莉負責的。她現在不在。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L35_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"점장이 하수인이면, 꼬마아가씨는 어떤 일을 하는데?","JPN":"店長が下僕なら、お嬢ちゃんはどんな仕事をしているの？","ENG":"If the manager is your subject, what do you do, little lady?","TWN":"如果店長是手下，那這位小妹妹是負責什麼的呢？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L36_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이 몸은 달콤한 주스를 만들 수 있노라.","JPN":"吾輩は甘いジュースを作れるのだ。","ENG":"I can make sweet juice.","TWN":"我負責製作香甜的果汁。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L37_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하긴. 이렇게 귀여우면 아무것도 안 해도 손님이 몰려들겠는걸?","JPN":"確かに。これだけ可愛いと、何もしなくてもお客さんが押し寄せてきそうね。","ENG":"I guess, being as cute as you are, you would still attract a large number of customers even if you did nothing.","TWN":"也對。你這麼可愛，就算什麼都不做，客人也會蜂擁而至吧？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L41_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"무엄햐구냐, 갸미 이 모메 볼을 자뱌 당기댜니.","JPN":"けしきゃらん、わがひゃいのほおをひっぴゃるとは。","ENG":"Hao dayr you. Hao dayr you pin'h ma sheeks la'ch dat?","TWN":"放肆！竟敢捏我的臉！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}}]`);export{e as default};